Petrobras to Keep Investments in Oil Refineries, Estado Says

-- B y   P e t e r   M i l l a r d
-- 
2011-06-30T18:49:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/petrobras-to-keep-investments-in-oil-refineries-estado-says.html
State-controlled  Petroleo Brasileiro
SA (PETR4)  will continue investing in four new oil refineries even as
the government asks the company to reduce its overall spending
in its proposed five-year business plan,  Agencia Estado 
reported, citing Energy Minister Edison Lobao.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Millard in  Rio de Janeiro  at 
 Pmillard1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at 
 dcrofts@bloomberg.net  